                        <img alt="Silk Dress Front" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" data-alt="A luxurious, high-fashion editorial shot of a deep navy blue silk slip dress displayed on a minimalist ivory mannequin. The dress drapes elegantly, showing off the smooth texture and bias cut. The background is a soft, pristine white studio setting with gentle, diffused natural lighting casting subtle shadows that emphasize the high-end modern aesthetic and premium craftsmanship." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAW_ouu4XJbcFzs9ebCNQXT8wtD4ao6kFG8pNMhW0zebKinZWyDCqjTRkKo54N0usX374XDfVzY02KXZmSPcYU085kvcc9uXhiHFcNvqcIzqy00CvO68WSbmHqK1hlWUF6CChDEltqvGgVa3mvCYcuKjJkOplFhqiiu8VjJF7ERWAOZnSgie7e2KQICyW1tLI8Rr-ev0PxbqAZO4lHnAWbcSJeJGkgx8VLFx7IX6YElByTunoonaBaZP6Ox0Ca0dF9FjvHFaK926vZR" />
